Step 3.2: Configure PC2 (Behind FW2 - IP: 10.20.0.2)
Open Terminal on Ubuntu PC2:

text
1. Press Ctrl+Alt+T to open terminal
2. Add route to remote network:
   sudo ip route add 10.10.10.0/24 via 10.20.0.1
