Part 5: Troubleshooting
Issue 1: Tunnel Status Shows "Down"
Navigation Path: VPN → IPsec Tunnels

text
Solution:
1. Click "Edit" on the tunnel
2. Click "Bring Up" button
3. Wait 10 seconds
4. Click "Refresh"
Issue 2: Phase 1 Down (IKE Gateway)
Navigation Path: Dashboard → CLI Console

bash
# Run this command
diagnose vpn ike gateway list
If you see "connecting" or nothing:

Possible Cause	Solution
Wrong Pre-shared Key	Verify both sides have identical PSK
Remote Gateway IP wrong	Check remote-gw matches other side's WAN IP
UDP 500 blocked	Ensure no firewall blocks UDP 500
Interface not up	Check port2 status is "UP"
